text: Lorene Derenty (born 4 September 1994) is a French water polo player. She was a member of the France women's national water polo team at the 2013 Summer Universiade, 2015 World Aquatics Championships, and 2017 World Aquatics Championships. == References == ==Other websites== * lorene-derenty * lorene- derenty-of-france Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:French water polo players Category:Aix-les-Bains Category:People from Savoie Category:Sportspeople from Auvergne-Rh√¥ne-Alpes
